  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to Labour community in Barisal Sadar in response to COVID-19 pandemic</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the project is to provide employees of transport services with multi-purpose cash support to address their basic needs. 
Due to the lockdown, transport owners are unable to provide their workers with daily wages, as all transportation services are suspended by the government authorities. Due to the specialised character of their work, transport employees were unable to seek different employment and therefore a particularly vulnerable group during the COVID-19 pandemic.</narrative>
  </description>
